08 Aug 2020 15:23






Great article overall! The dialogue was believable, and for such an upbeat scip, the message was clear and serious. The one thing that could be improved is the progression. I would have liked to see a bit more of the consequences of environmental negligence in the park, whether sprinkled throughout the narrative or having a new chunk added in the middle.

Either way, this was a great scip. +1 from me any day.







